@node "Intro_REGISTER" "How to become a registered user of COMPACT"
This program is released under the shareware concept. This means, that you
have to pay a shareware fee, and thus becoming a registered user of this
program. When you are registered, you will receive a personalised keyfile.

In this keyfile your name, your address and a serial number is stored, and
with this file, which must be in the S: directory, the demo version of the
program will become automatically the full working version with no features
disabled anymore.
This has the advantage for you, that in the case of an update you can get
the newest demo version from the Aminet or the like, and together with your
keyfile you automatically will have the newest full working version. However
please note, that the author is not _obliged_ to publish updates of this
program, although this is planned for the future! The author reserves its
right to reject a registration request.


@{B}Please note also, that you are not allowed to distribute the keyfile to an
other person / firm etc.! Only the author of this program is allowed to
distribute keyfiles!@{UB} If a keyfile is spread in an illegal way to other
persons, the author can cancel the validity of it, so in the next update this
keyfile will be useless, and the author knows the user who spread it, so
further consequences will be possible!


@{U}@{B}IMPORTANT NOTE:@{UU}@{UB}

I can not guarantee that the player will work on _EVERY_ CDROM drive, because
i have only a few drives available for testing. Of course you can choose,
which device-name and unit will be used, and in most cases it will work. But
if you own a drive, which does NOT work with the player, you should NOT send
me money for the registration, because i am not able to solve this problem!
Sorry about this, but it is nearly impossible for me to make your drive
working with my player, so if your drive is one of these, please try to use
an other player program!


@{U}The following cripples are active, as long as the program is not registered:@{UU}

- At the start of the player a window will open with the info that you use
  the demo version.
- You only can use the program for 15 minutes. After this time, the program
  will send a "STOP"-command to the CD-ROM drive and quit.
- The proportional slider only can be moved in the mode "Actual Title". In
  the other modes you can only see the position of it, but no movement will
  be possible.
- The ARexx port is not available.
- The database can manage only up to 30 entries.
- The hotkeys to control COMPACT from nearly every multitasking program are
  limited to PLAY, STOP and POPUP.
- The "JUMP" button only can jump to positions below 16 minutes.


@{B}@{U}How to register:@{UB}@{UU}

When you want to receive your keyfile with @{B}email@{UB}, the price for a
registered version of COMPACT is 10,- DM (German Marks),  5,- EURO,
or 6,- US $ (US-Dollar); no other currencies please.

When you want to receive your keyfile with @{B}disk via normal mail@{UB}, the
price for a registered version of COMPACT is 14,- DM (German Marks),
7,- EURO, or 8,- US $ (US-Dollar); no other currencies please.


Getting the money to @{"me" LINK Intro_Author} is not simple, since most
banks charge a lot for foreign money transfers. Here are some options:

- Sending cash (preferred). This is the most succesful way of getting
  money across. When sending US $, please only send paper-money, because
  i can't change coins in a foreign currency on my bank. Of course,
  when sending DM (or EURO) it is a good idea too to send paper-money,
  because it is not as heavy as coins. Be sure cash is not detectable from
  outside the envelope!
  If you feel insecure about mailing money, most post-offices offer a
  service that will report back to you that everything safely arrived
  at my place. However please note, that it is your own risk to send cash,
  so i am not responsible when the money disappears on the way to me.

- Within Europe, send an EuroCheque (in DM or EURO). I believe there are no
  costs for this, but check locally. Make sure you mark "DM" or "EURO" as
  currency, and don't forget to fill out the EuroCheque completely (card
  number on the back of the cheque for example).

Do **NOT** send CHEQUES, MONEY ORDERs or similar methods of payment!!

If you do not take transfer costs into account and the final amount of
money is less than the price mentioned above, you'll have to do yet another
transfer before you can get your registered version of the keyfile.

The delivery will be as soon as possible, but please allow me a few weeks
for delivery, because i'm not at home all the time (holiday, business
trips etc.), so please be patient. If you already own COMPACT, and you
only need a keyfile, you can get it via E-Mail. In this case, delivery will
be of course faster (and cheaper) than sending a disk. You can state this
in the form for registering:

IN ALL CASES PLEASE USE THE PROVIDED @{"FORM FOR REGISTERING" LINK Orderform/Main} AND SEND IT
TO ME! Of course, your data will be handled confidentially. If you don't
own a printer, you also can write the contents of this form to a letter
and fill out its contents. Please fill out the form legible, esspecially
your address and your E-Mail address!


  @{"My address" LINK Intro_Author}


@endnode

